pull.title: [qt] Rename formateNiceTimeOffset(qint64) to formatNiceTimeOffset(qint64)
pull.body:
Rename `formateNiceTimeOffset(qint64)` to `formatNiceTimeOffset(qint64)`.

The **e** in "format**e**" is most likely a typo :-)
